        {
          "@type": "Review",
          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "Nigel Carlisle"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I participated in a woodland photography workshop this weekend. Alan offered great advice and patience, taking time to explain everything in layman’s terms. After an interesting slideshow we entered the woodland to the rear of his property. Alan suggested suitable opportunities to set up our tripods and endeavour to capture the perfect shot. With his considerable knowledge and professional approach, I would strongly recommend one of these workshops, particularly if you want to take control of your camera rather than relying on the auto setting!",
          "reviewRating": {
