          "author": {
            "@type": "Person",
            "name": "David Proctor"
          },
          "reviewBody": "I have done two workshops with Alan and both have been excellent. His teaching style is very much geared to the individual participants and the workshop numbers are limited so that everyone gets the amount of time / help that they need. His knowledge, both technical and of the locations used, is second to none. If anyone is considering doing a photography workshop I would have no hesitation whatsoever in recommending Alan.",
